org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.filespecs

Interface IZipFileSpecification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, IFileSpecification
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ZipFileSpecification

    public interface IZipFileSpecification
extends IFileSpecification, Closeable
    Interface for dealing with zip files. Since SWCs are actually zip files,this provides an additional way to deal with files that doesn't involve mxmlc
